high_descs: Take a step then turn right and walk to then turn left and walk to the middle of the coffee table on your left turning left to face it when you get there and walk close to it.
Pick up the box on the coffee table,
Turn left and walk to the tv stand then turn right and walk to the chair.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box on the chair.

high_descs: Turn right at the black chair and go around the white coffee table to the black couch beside it.
Pick up the box on the white table.
Circle back around the left side of the coffee table to the black chair in the corner.
Put the box in the black chair.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the box and put it in the black chair.

high_descs: Put the box on the couch
anns.task_desc: Move a box to a couch
